description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment to provide a building comprising four interlinked blocks above a double height 'podium' rising from ground plus eight storeys to ground plus 12 storeys to include 86 residential units and three retail units (within either Class A1 or A2). Three basement levels comprising residential leisure facilities, storage, servicing, parking and cycle bay provision, together with parking, leisure and servicing facilities for adjacent hotel. Relocation of Edinburgh Gate and realignment of Knightsbridge; associated highways works and the stopping up of existing public highways. Reorientation of the Knightsbridge underground staircase/entrance (north side) and all necessary enabling works.
